| owner = [[David Richards (racing)|David Richards]]&lt;br/&gt;John Sinders&lt;br/&gt;[[Investment Dar]]&lt;br/&gt;Adeem Investment&lt;ref name=&quot;NewShareholders&quot;&gt;{{cite web|url=http://www.astonmartin.com/thecompany/news?a=1a77ab65-8f1a-4793-b988-6fc0f2882719 |title=The Company - News |publisher=Aston Martin |date=2007-03-12 |accessdate=2009-04-29}}&lt;/ref&gt;
