==DVD release==
The first seven episodes were released on [[DVD]] on May 30, 2006 in [[Region 1]] from [[Lions Gate Home Entertainment]] in a single-disc release entitled ''ALF and The Beanstalk and Other Classic Fairy Tales''. There is yet to be a complete series DVD of the whole series.

