== Politics ==
Aalen has arranged a [[municipal association]] with [[Essingen]] and [[Hüttlingen, Baden-Württemberg|Hüttlingen]].

=== City council ===
Since the [[local election]] of 7&amp;nbsp;June&amp;nbsp;2009, the [[municipal council|city council]] consists of 54&amp;nbsp;representatives having a five year’s term of office. The seats are distributed as follows on parties and groups (changes refer to the second last election of 2004):

