      <text xml:space="preserve">{{Infobox medical person
|Aloysius Alzheimer       =Aloysius Alzheimer
|image                   =Alois Alzheimer 003.jpg
|caption                 =Alois Alzheimer 
|birth_date              ={{birth date|1864|6|14|mf=y}}
|birth_place             =[[Marktbreit]], [[Bavaria]]
|death_date              ={{death date and age|1915|12|19|1864|6|14|mf=y}}
|death_place             =[[Wrocław|Breslau]], [[Germany]]
 (now [[Wrocław]], [[Poland]])
|profession              =[[Psychiatrist]], [[Physician]]
