      </contributor>
      <minor />
      <comment>r2.7.1) (robot Adding: [[jv:Akio Morita]]</comment>
      <text xml:space="preserve">{{Infobox person
|name        = Akio Morita                 
|image       = 
|image_size  = 
|caption     = 
|birth_name  = 
|birth_date  = {{Birth date|1921|1|26}}
|birth_place = [[Nagoya, Aichi]], [[Japan]]&lt;ref&gt;[http://www.akiomorita.net/en/profile/life.html Chronology] About Akio Morita, Akio Morita Library&lt;/ref&gt;
